Schering-Plough Corp. said it combined its Schering Laboratories' domestic over-the-counter business and the company's personal-care group into a new entity, Schering-Plough HealthCare Products. 

David E. Collins, the executive vice president responsible for these businesses, becomes president of the new unit. 

Schering-Plough also renamed its Pharmaceutical Operations to Schering-Plough Pharmaceuticals, with Donald R. Conklin, executive vice president, assuming the title of president of that unit. 

